  "body": "I followed this wiki: https://github.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/wiki/Setting-up-private-network-or-local-cluster\n\nBut since the title is `Setting up private network`. I think it should include the flag `--nodiscover`, because it is **very** confusing if you do `net.peerCount` and see more than 2 nodes, when the tutorial is about exactly 2 nodes initially.\n",
